OL,3,COne dead and eight hospitalised due to
OL,4,C'unusually strong' batch of heroin
OL,6,FA man has died and eight others have
OL,7,Fundergone hospital treatment after an
OL,8,F'unusually strong' batch of heroin was
OL,9,Fcirculated in North Devon.
OL,11,FAt around 5pm on Friday 26 April, were
OL,12,Fnotified of the drug being used across
OL,13,FWestward Ho!, Bideford and Barnstaple.
OL,15,FBy midnight that evening, eight people
OL,16,Fhad been treated in hospital after
OL,17,Fthey had believed to have taken the
OL,18,FClass A drug.
