OL,3,COne dead and eight hospitalised due to
OL,4,C'unusually strong' batch of heroin
OL,6,FA ninth person, a man, then died after
OL,7,Fhaving taken a substance, believed to
OL,8,Fbe the heroin.
OL,10,FOfficers declared a major incident due
OL,11,Fto the threat posed by the drug. This
OL,12,Fhas now been stood down on 27 April.
OL,14,FFollowing police investigations, two
OL,15,Fmen and two women have been arrested
OL,16,Fon suspicion of being involved in the
OL,17,Fsupply of a controlled substance.
OL,19,FAll currently remain in police custody.
