OL,3,COne dead and eight hospitalised due to
OL,4,C'unusually strong' batch of heroin
OL,6,FNorth and West Devon local policing
OL,7,Farea commander Superintendent Toby
OL,8,FDavies said: "As soon as we were made
OL,9,Faware of the issue this substance was
OL,10,Flikely to cause on Friday evening, we
OL,11,Fdid everything possible with partners
OL,12,Fto reach out to the drug using
OL,13,Fcommunity to warn them of potential
OL,14,Fdanger they were facing.
OL,16,F"We continue to work with health
OL,17,Fpartners to warn those who may be
OL,18,Fsubstance users to exercise extreme
OL,19,Fcaution. However, we would reassure
OL,20,Fthe community we believe this is now
OL,21,Fcontained.
