OL,6,FThe College of Policing defines a
OL,7,Fmajor incident as "an event or
OL,8,Fsituation requiring a response under
OL,9,Fone or more of the emergency services'
OL,10,Fmajor incident plans" and one that
OL,11,F"will usually include involving large
OL,12,Fnumbers of people, either directly or
OL,13,Findirectly."
